{"title":"洪水退去之后（外一首）","authors":["浦学坤"],"dates":[{"year":1991,"month":10,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"洪水退去之后（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浦学坤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨击浪卷，也有疲惫的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被水妖睡过的木床"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哽咽住暮色的苍茫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那些斑驳的房屋、树干"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把一个惊心动魄的故事"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收藏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"度过多雨的七月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在痛苦中锻造出纯朴的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"激昂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"思绪搀扶着月色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏响长堤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尝过洪水的苦涩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"崛起无数古铜般脊梁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被水浸湿的翅膀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沉重地飞翔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驮起中天之日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照临一个大写风韵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"信念之魂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灿烂而辉煌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"治水哲思"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江河饱饮混浊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石头沉寂于苦涩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"女娲长眠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们咏叹大禹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五千年握在手里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依旧沉甸甸一个水字"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要筑就筑吧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用情感、聪慧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用各种特殊材料"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"筑起浑厚淳朴的大堤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要炸就炸吧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用理智、博大"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用自我牺牲精神"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炸开结构精妙的大坝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"屈伸自如的手指"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"逼退洪浪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千百年的传说延续后裔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在历史久久的注视中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人，面对水族"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总会走进去再走出来"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}